# {{legal}} A [[tort]] [[cause of action]] that arises where a [[party]] is injured because the other party [[entrust]]ed a [[dangerous]] [[instrumentality]] (such as a [[vehicle]] or a [[weapon]]) to a person whom the other party knew or reasonably should have known should not be trusted with that instrumentality.

